com.module.interaction

接口 RXTXListener


  • public interface RXTXListener
    Implement this interface who want to listen sending data to reader,receiving data from reader,and the connection missing with reader.

    • 方法概要

      所有方法 实例方法 抽象方法 
      限定符和类型 方法和说明
      void onLostConnect()
      This method will callback when the monitor thread of data returned by reader is quit.
      void reciveData(byte[] btAryReceiveData)
      This method will callback when the reader receive the data returned by reader.
      void sendData(byte[] btArySendData)
      This method will callback when the reader send the data returned by reader.

    • 方法详细资料

      • reciveData

        void reciveData(byte[] btAryReceiveData)
        This method will callback when the reader receive the data returned by reader. You can monitor the raw data return from reader via override it. And this method running in child thread.
        参数:
        btAryReceiveData - return data.

      • sendData

        void sendData(byte[] btArySendData)
        This method will callback when the reader send the data returned by reader. You can monitor the raw data send to reader via override it.
        参数:
        btArySendData - the send data to reader.

      • onLostConnect

        void onLostConnect()
        This method will callback when the monitor thread of data returned by reader is quit. You can monitor it to do something when the monitor thread of data returned by reader quit. And this method running in child thread.
